{"tid":2226783,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"30歲躉船船員葵涌墮海溺斃 消防撈起全身僵硬","createTime":"2020-10-02T08:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T09:35:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"267fce215e1354fac851cfdd7c2a7043c7a944d6","tid":2226783,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T08:46:29.000Z","msg":"一名年約30歲船員，中午前在葵涌醉酒灣公眾碼頭卸貨區躉船上墮海，約兩小時後被消防蛙人救起證實不治。警方正調查墮海原因。<br />\n<br />\n警方早上11時許接報後，消防派出蛙人到場搜索，到下午1時許在碼頭對開海面發現事主，但救起時已全身僵硬，送到青衣滅火輪消防局經檢驗後證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\nsource: 頭條"},{"pid":"962b3e52582f0368e8821603c4655106d7a4fe6c","tid":2226783,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T08:47:31.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8128c8d738cac992d19f5729f2fc972fe9fd991","tid":2226783,"uid":116530,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T08:48:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9f3d32c3482c1bba98df4692e78ca7ea505a3b4","tid":2226783,"uid":116696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T08:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd692f0bcefc212f7ba03790f1613949201360f8","tid":2226783,"uid":362346,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T09:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets